    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a serious project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust along the wheel wells and frame, alongside faded paint and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul as it currently struggles to idle and has multiple fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, the headliner is sagging, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. It will likely need to be towed from the lot and will require substantial investment to be roadworthy again.",
