    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look or have any questions!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle exhibits strong mechanical synergy, with recent preventative maintenance addressing the critical VANOS system and rod bearings. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from an inspected rear subframe and refreshed suspension geometry for optimal turn-in. While showing signs of honest use, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power and a visceral exhaust note through the quad-exit system. A mechanically sound example ready for the technical B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean title. Mechanically sound. Minor cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
