      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this reliable beauty. It\u2019s been such a great ride for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next chapter with a new owner. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love how it handles. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 28900.0,
