    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2017 BMW M2, a true F87-generation athlete. At its heart is the N55B30T0 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six, delivering 365 hp through a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission with Drivelogic. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by the Active M Differential and forged 19-inch Style 437M wheels. This example features a high-flow intake and has been monitored for common N55 vulnerabilities, including a verified oil filter housing gasket and upgraded charge pipe. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing the M3/M4-derived aluminum subframes and control arms. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is linear and aggressive. A compelling entry into M-ownership for the serious driver.",
